---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const title = "转山路线 | Kailash 2026";
const description = "冈仁波齐52公里转山路线完整攻略：三天标准行程、两天挑战行程、一天极限行程。13个补给站详细信息，海拔、距离、路况全掌握。";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <div class="pt-20">
    <!-- Hero -->
    <section class="bg-kailash-dark py-16">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4" data-lang-content="zh">转山路线</h1>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Kora Routes</h1>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">コーラルート</h1>
        <h1 class="font-display text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-white mb-4" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">코라 루트</h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/80" data-lang-content="zh">52公里 sacred circuit · 13个补给站 · 3种行程方案</p>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/80" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">52km sacred circuit · 13 supply stations · 3 itinerary options</p>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/80" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">52km 聖なる巡礼路 · 13の補給所 · 3つの行程プラン</p>
        <p class="text-xl text-white/80" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">52km 신성한 순례길 · 13개 보급소 · 3가지 일정</p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Route Plans -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-kailash-light">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
          <!-- 3-Day Standard -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
            <div class="p-6 bg-blue-100 border-b">
              <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="zh">三天转山</h2>
              <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">3-Day Kora</h2>
              <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">三日間コーラ</h2>
              <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">삼일 코라</h2>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1" data-lang-content="zh">标准行程 · 适合大多数朝圣者</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Standard · For most pilgrims</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">標準行程 · 大多数の巡礼者に適する</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">표준 일정 · 대부분의 순례자에게 적합</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-4 text-center">
                <div><p class="text-lg font-bold text-kailash-gold">52km</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="zh">距离</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Distance</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">距離</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">거리</p></div>
                <div><p class="text-lg font-bold text-kailash-gold">3天2夜</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="zh">时长</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Duration</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">期間</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">기간</p></div>
                <div><p class="text-lg font-bold text-blue-600">中等</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="zh">难度</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Difficulty</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">難易度</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">난이도</p></div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4" data-lang-content="zh">最经典的转山行程。第一天适应海拔，第二天翻越垭口，第三天轻松返程。</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">The classic Kora. Day 1 for altitude adaptation, Day 2 for pass crossing, Day 3 easy return.</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">最も古典的なコーラ行程。初日は標高順化、二日目は峠越え、三日目は楽な帰路。</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">가장 전통적인 코라 일정. 첫날 해발 적응, 둘째 날 고개 넘기, 셋째 날 편안한 귀로.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 2-Day Challenge -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
            <div class="p-6 bg-red-100 border-b">
              <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="zh">两天转山</h2>
              <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">2-Day Kora</h2>
              <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">二日間コーラ</h2>
              <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">이일 코라</h2>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1" data-lang-content="zh">挑战极限 · 适合体能好的朝圣者</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Challenging · For experienced trekkers</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">挑戦的 · 体力に自信のある巡礼者向け</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">도전적 · 체력이 좋은 순례자용</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-4 text-center">
                <div><p class="text-lg font-bold text-kailash-gold">52km</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="zh">距离</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Distance</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">距離</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">거리</p></div>
                <div><p class="text-lg font-bold text-kailash-gold">2天1夜</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="zh">时长</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Duration</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">期間</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">기간</p></div>
                <div><p class="text-lg font-bold text-red-600">困难</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="zh">难度</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Difficulty</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">難易度</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">난이도</p></div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4" data-lang-content="zh">第一天走到止热寺，第二天凌晨出发翻越垭口直接返回。第二天强度极大。</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Day 1 to Drirapuk, Day 2 early start crossing Drolma La and return. Extremely demanding second day.</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">初日はディラプク寺まで、二日目は早朝出発で峠を越えて直接帰る。二日目の負荷は極めて大きい。</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">첫날 디라푹 사원까지, 둘째 날 새벽 출발해 고개를 넘어 바로 귀환. 둘째 날 부담이 매우 큼.</p>
              <p class="text-red-600 text-sm bg-red-50 p-3 rounded-lg" data-lang-content="zh">⚠️ 第二天需行走30公里且翻越5648米垭口，不建议初次转山者选择</p>
              <p class="text-red-600 text-sm bg-red-50 p-3 rounded-lg" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">⚠️ Day 2 requires 30km with 5648m pass. Not recommended for first-time pilgrims.</p>
              <p class="text-red-600 text-sm bg-red-50 p-3 rounded-lg" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">⚠️ 二日目は30km・5648m峠越え。初めての巡礼者には非推奨。</p>
              <p class="text-red-600 text-sm bg-red-50 p-3 rounded-lg" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">⚠️ 둘째 날 30km·5648m 고개 넘기. 처음 하는 순례자에게 비추천.</p>
            </div>
          </div>

          <!-- 1-Day Extreme -->
          <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-lg overflow-hidden">
            <div class="p-6 bg-purple-100 border-b">
              <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="zh">一天转山</h2>
              <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">1-Day Kora</h2>
              <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">一日コーラ</h2>
              <h2 class="font-display text-2xl font-bold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">일일 코라</h2>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1" data-lang-content="zh">极限挑战 · 仅限资深朝圣者</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Extreme · For elite athletes only</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">極限挑戦 · 上級巡礼者のみ</p>
              <p class="text-sm text-gray-600 mt-1" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">극한 도전 · 고급 순례자 전용</p>
            </div>
            <div class="p-6">
              <div class="grid grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-4 text-center">
                <div><p class="text-lg font-bold text-kailash-gold">52km</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="zh">距离</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Distance</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">距離</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">거리</p></div>
                <div><p class="text-lg font-bold text-kailash-gold">12-22h</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="zh">时长</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Duration</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">期間</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">기간</p></div>
                <div><p class="text-lg font-bold text-purple-600">极限</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="zh">难度</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Difficulty</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">難易度</p><p class="text-xs text-gray-500" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">난이도</p></div>
              </div>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4" data-lang-content="zh">一天内完成52公里外转，对体能、海拔适应力和意志力都是终极考验。</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Completing 52km in one day. Ultimate test of fitness, altitude adaptation, and willpower.</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">一日で52kmを完走。体力・高地順化力・意志の究極の試練。</p>
              <p class="text-gray-600 text-sm mb-4" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">하루에 52km 완주. 체력·고적응력·의지의 궁극적인 시험.</p>
              <p class="text-red-600 text-sm bg-red-50 p-3 rounded-lg" data-lang-content="zh">⚠️ 极高风险！每年均有救援案例。普通游客绝对禁止尝试！</p>
              <p class="text-red-600 text-sm bg-red-50 p-3 rounded-lg" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">⚠️ Extremely high risk! Rescue cases every year. Ordinary tourists must NOT attempt!</p>
              <p class="text-red-600 text-sm bg-red-50 p-3 rounded-lg" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">⚠️ 極めて高リスク！毎年救助事例あり。一般観光客は絶対に試さないでください！</p>
              <p class="text-red-600 text-sm bg-red-50 p-3 rounded-lg" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">⚠️ 극도로 높은 위험! 매년 구조 사례. 일반 관광객은 절대 시도하지 마세요!</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- 3-Day Details -->
    <section class="py-16 bg-white">
      <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-8 text-center" data-lang-content="zh">三天标准行程详情</h2>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-8 text-center" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">3-Day Standard Itinerary</h2>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-8 text-center" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">三日間標準行程詳細</h2>
        <h2 class="font-display text-3xl font-bold text-kailash-dark mb-8 text-center" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">삼일 표준 일정 상세</h2>
        
        <div class="space-y-8">
          <!-- Day 1 -->
          <div class="bg-kailash-light rounded-2xl p-8">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-kailash-gold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-kailash-dark font-bold text-xl">1</div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="zh">塔尔钦 → 止热寺</h3>
                <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Darchen → Drirapuk</h3>
                <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">タルチェン → ディラプク寺</h3>
                <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">타르첸 → 디라푹 사원</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">22km · 4600m→5200m · 6-8h</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4" data-lang-content="zh">从塔尔钦出发，经曲古寺，沿拉曲河谷上行，最终抵达止热寺。这是适应海拔的第一天，路况相对平缓。</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Depart from Darchen, pass Choku Gompa, follow Lhaqu Valley upstream to Drirapuk. Gentle terrain for altitude adaptation.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">タルチェンを出発、曲古寺を経て、ラ曲河谷を遡上し、最終的にディラプク寺に到着。標高順化の初日、比較的平坦な道。</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">타르첸 출발, 쿠쿠 사원을 지나, 라취 계곡을 따라 올라가 디라푹 사원에 도착. 해발 적응의 첫날, 비교적 평탄한 길.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3">
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="zh">曲古寺</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Choku Gompa</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">曲古寺</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">쿠쿠 사원</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="zh">玛尼堆群</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Mani Stones</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">マニ石群</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">마니석 군</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="zh">止热寺（住宿点）</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Drirapuk (Lodging)</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">ディラプク寺（宿泊）</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">디라푹 사원 (숙박)</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 p-3 rounded-lg" data-lang-content="zh">💡 第一天不要走太快，给身体适应海拔的时间。止热寺是唯一住宿点，旺季需提前确认床位。</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 p-3 rounded-lg" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">💡 Don't rush on Day 1. Allow time for altitude adaptation. Drirapuk is the only lodging—confirm availability.</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 p-3 rounded-lg" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">💡 初日は急がないで、標高順化の時間を与える。ディラプク寺は唯一の宿泊所、繁忙期は事前確認を。</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 p-3 rounded-lg" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">💡 첫날 서두르지 마세요. 해발 적응 시간을 허용하세요. 디라푹 사원은 유일한 숙소, 성수기는 사전 확인.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Day 2 -->
          <div class="bg-kailash-light rounded-2xl p-8">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
              <div class="w-12 h-12 bg-kailash-gold rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-kailash-dark font-bold text-xl">2</div>
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="zh">止热寺 → 尊最普寺</h3>
                <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Drirapuk → Zunzhepu</h3>
                <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">ディラプク寺 → ゾンチュプ寺</h3>
                <h3 class="font-display text-xl font-bold text-kailash-dark" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">디라푹 사원 → 존츄푸 사원</h3>
                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">18km · 5200m→5648m→4800m · 8-10h</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4" data-lang-content="zh">最艰难的一天。凌晨出发翻越5648米的卓玛拉垭口，这是整个转山路线最高点。下山经过托吉错，最终抵达尊最普寺。</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">The hardest day. Depart early to cross 5648m Drolma La, the highest point. Descend past Tsoji Lake to Zunzhepu.</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">最も厳しい一日。早朝出発で5648mのドマラ峠を越える、これが最高点。下山してトジ錯を経てゾンチュプ寺に到着。</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">가장 힘든 하루. 새벽 출발해 5648m 도마라 고개를 넘는, 이것이 최고점. 하산하여 토지 호를 지나 존츄푸 사원에 도착.</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3">
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="zh">卓玛拉垭口（5648m）</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Drolma La (5648m)</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">ドマラ峠（5648m）</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">도마라 고개 (5648m)</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="zh">托吉错</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Tsoji Lake</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">トジ錯</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">토지 호</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="zh">尊最普寺（住宿点）</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Zunzhepu (Lodging)</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">ゾンチュプ寺（宿泊）</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">존츄푸 사원 (숙박)</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 p-3 rounded-lg" data-lang-content="zh">💡 垭口前1公里最陡，保持节奏；下山保护膝盖。尊最普寺住宿条件比止热寺更简陋。</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 p-3 rounded-lg" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">💡 The 1km before the pass is steepest—pace yourself. Protect knees on descent. Zunzhepu lodging is more basic.</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 p-3 rounded-lg" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">💡 峠前1kmが最も急、ペースを保つ。下山時は膝を保護。ゾンチュプ寺の宿泊設備はより簡素。</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 p-3 rounded-lg" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">💡 고개 전 1km가 가장 가파름, 페이스 유지. 하산 시 무릎 보호. 존츄푸 사원 숙소는 더 간소함.</p>
          </div>

          <!-- Day 3 -->
          <div class="bg-kailash-light rounded-2xl p-8">
            <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
