                <p class="text-sm text-gray-500">14km · 4800m→4600m · 3-4h</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4" data-lang-content="zh">轻松的一天，沿峡谷平缓下降，回到塔尔钦，完成转山。胜利在望！</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Easy day with gentle descent through the canyon back to Darchen. Victory is near!</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">楽な一日、峡谷を緩やかに下ってタルチェンに戻る。勝利が目前！</p>
            <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">편안한 하루, 협곡을 따라 천천히 내려가 타르첸으로 돌아간다. 승리가 코앞!</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2 mb-3">
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="zh">峡谷风光</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Canyon Scenery</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">峡谷の風景</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">협곡 풍경</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="zh">玛旁雍错远眺</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Lake Manasarovar View</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">マナサロワール湖遠望</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">마나사로와르 호 원경</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="zh">塔尔钦（终点）</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">Darchen (Finish)</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">タルチェン（終点）</span>
              <span class="bg-kailash-gold/20 text-kailash-dark px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">타르첸 (종점)</span>
            </div>
            <p class="text-sm text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 p-3 rounded-lg" data-lang-content="zh">💡 胜利在望，但不要大意，注意脚下安全。回到塔尔钦后可以好好吃一顿，庆祝转山完成！</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 p-3 rounded-lg" data-lang-content="en" style="display: none;">💡 Victory is near but stay careful—watch your step. Celebrate with a good meal back in Darchen!</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 p-3 rounded-lg" data-lang-content="ja" style="display: none;">💡 勝利が目前だが油断せず、足元に注意。タルチェンに戻って美味しい食事で祝おう！</p>
            <p class="text-sm text-blue-600 bg-blue-50 p-3 rounded-lg" data-lang-content="ko" style="display: none;">💡 승리가 코앞이지만 방심하지 말고, 발밑에 주의. 타르첸에 돌아가 맛있는 식사로 축하하자!</p>
          </div>
